        <Parent_String>Castilian (group of languages) [300411877], Western Iberian (languages) [300411876], Ibero-Romance (languages) [300411875], Western Romance (languages) [300411872], Italo-Western (languages) [300411871], Romance (languages) [300411870], Italic (languages) [300388475], Indo-European (language family) [300388458], languages and writing systems by specific type [300389738], languages and writing systems [300389739], language-related concepts [300263371], Associated Concepts (hierarchy name) [300055126], Associated Concepts Facet [300264086]</Parent_String>
